{"tid":1781446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[搬錢有效？］花旗銀行(香港)第三季存款按年度增長10%","createTime":"2019-12-13T07:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T11:37:06.000Z","uid":185424,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2112dbe91568744318f575fec523f27f15fa0dc4","tid":1781446,"uid":185424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:08:35.000Z","msg":"唔知同大家手足係咁搬錢有無關，搞到花旗beat target<br />\n大家要繼續，唔好俾佢停<br />\n寧願益美帝，都唔好益中資<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Business<br />\n<br />\nCitigroup Gives Extra Day Off in Hong Kong, Sees Beating Targets</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nCitigroup will give all its staff in Hong Kong an extra day off next year, saying it&rsquo;s on track to surpass revenue targets even as pro-Democracy protests roiled the city over the past six months.<br />\nIn a memo to staff seen by Bloomberg on Friday, the U.S. bank&rsquo;s local chief executive officer, Angel Ng, thanked the staff for working through &ldquo;extreme difficulty.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Many of you went the extra mile to ensure that our operations and services remain uninterrupted during disruptions,&rdquo; she said in the memo, which was confirmed by a spokesman at the bank.<br />\n<br />\nThe financial hub is the bank&rsquo;s fourth biggest market globally by revenue. Deal making in the city has persevered during the unprecedented turmoil, highlighted by a massive listing last month by Alibaba Group Holding Ltd., even as Hong Kong&rsquo;s economy has plunged into a recession.<br />\nNg said in the memo that the bank&rsquo;s Hong Kong business is on track to beat revenue targets in the fourth quarter and in the full year. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Third quarter revenue rose 8%, driven by 10% increase in average deposits while loans rose 6%</span></strong>, according to separate memo from Ng in October.<br />\n<br />\nStrain has been felt by banking staff across the city, with frequent demonstrations largely shutting its downtown financial area. Citigroup was directly affected when one of its investment bankers was detained following a scuffle with police.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/amp/news/articles/2019-12-13/citigroup-gives-extra-day-off-in-hong-kong-sees-beating-targets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-12-13%2Fcitigroup-gives-extra-day-off-in-hong-kong-sees-beating-targets&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6gb0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=989003f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/amp/news/articles/2019-12-13/citigroup-gives-extra-day-off-in-hong-kong-sees-beating-targets</a>"},{"pid":"59bc114155762628d3e9da917186f4f9ab5b192c","tid":1781446,"uid":185424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aeed5642a6c03643e27dc0b3fa47c6f36958b7bf","tid":1781446,"uid":78047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a89c6d86a1cc1232297c7813304d83c27d1132","tid":1781446,"uid":138609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:25:06.000Z","msg":"真係驚金融不穩 要離岸先有用<br />\n即使香港注冊外資<br />\n港共一樣有權要求強制結匯<br />\n只不過叫做唔俾支資賺錢咁解<br />\n不過除左花旗外都無好選擇<br />\n匯豐渣打都咁黑人憎"},{"pid":"14fda5ac1610b4b3587c34e5687d6ea921403caa","tid":1781446,"uid":185424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99a89c6d86a1cc1232297c7813304d83c27d1132","tid":1781446,"uid":138609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:25:06.